{"tid":1847323,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"政府停工只係唔想自私公務員未來參與罷工","createTime":"2020-01-28T04:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T04:36:00.000Z","uid":192851,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9a2ae405c37d035e6df63d49d56f8711fea265e0","tid":1847323,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:26:20.000Z","msg":"而家疫情愈來愈嚴重，如果真係為左防疫而停工，咁係咪應該停到五月？<span style=\"color: red;\">五月peak嗰時係咪宵禁埋？</span><br />\n<br />\n說到底，支共政府唔會主動封關，所以諗唔到有咩有用既野可以做<br />\n<br />\n加上公務員主要都係自私藍，<span style=\"color: red;\">停佢地工會令佢地自私地覺得政府做左啲令佢地自己安全啲既野</span><br />\n<br />\n喺粉嶺一役見到黃藍合作會係一個好恐怖嘅Pandora Box，唔可以比全港人知道暴力先有用，<span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以比公務員跟隊帶住怨氣一齊罷工</span><br />\n<br />\n廢總結: 而家未算社區爆發，沿頭係所有支那人，唔封關係幫助唔到疫情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4661d3b2e89a9989449b6a2d2e0b610ac701690c","tid":1847323,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:26:48.000Z","msg":"罷工"},{"pid":"c9466bb54a3dffd204b8fe0a0bdf26529d8f9331","tid":1847323,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"罷佢老母"},{"pid":"89cce56a2cf5b281a18a36062c770b5817cad07a","tid":1847323,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"醫護、入境、海關、衞生署成為condom<br />\n高官及文職同你地割蔗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得佢地要對住大劣人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pd0xhvm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPd0xhvm.jpg&h=e650018e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"55d927fc0b6c118507032b6127c8be653c2dd937","tid":1847323,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"三罷"},{"pid":"3f385bb23065cf28a